%%{init: {"theme": "base"}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Candidato
    participant A as Agente IA
    participant W as Playwright
    participant R as reports/
    participant G as generate-pdf.mjs
    participant T as merge-tracker.mjs
    participant D as data/applications.md

    U->>A: Cola URL ou texto JD
    alt URL
        A->>W: browser_navigate + snapshot
        W-->>A: Texto JD
    else Texto direto
        A->>A: Usa JD do chat
    end

    A->>A: Lê cv.md, profile.yml, _shared.md
    A->>A: Avaliação A–G + score
    A->>R: Grava reports/NNN-company-date.md

    alt output_format = latex
        A->>A: Pipeline LaTeX (generate-latex.mjs)
    else default HTML
        A->>G: HTML → PDF
        G-->>A: output/cv-*.pdf
    end

    opt score >= 4.5
        A->>W: Snapshot formulário (se URL)
        A->>R: Adiciona seção H (rascunho)
    end

    A->>A: Escreve batch/tracker-additions/*.tsv
    A->>T: merge-tracker.mjs
    T->>D: Consolida linha no tracker
    A-->>U: Resumo: score, PDF, recomendação
